  <h1 class="indent">Le-Kit Documentation</h1>
  <p>
    Welcome to the documentation for Le-Kit, a library of web components designed to help your users to easily build consistent and accessible user interfaces. Here you'll find guides and examples to help you get started with using Le-Kit in your projects.
  </p>

  <h3 class="indent">It's a Work in Progress!</h3>
  <p>I have to warn you, that this is really early stage for the library. The installation process, the way you should copy the required assets, the way you should structure the styles for your project, and the API of the components are all definitely going to change.</p>
  <p>Feel free to participate and provide feedback or contribute to the project in the GitHub repo:</p>

